rComments: This course is more toward forensic investigation and court presentations, if your research needs some fresh HFE science with todays technology... this is not a good place for you. Professor gives a chance to purchase her own book in the class, but that text book is outdated, be careful to take this course, she may fail you!!!

Prof Smiley is rather monotonous, but she is definitely an expert in human factors as she has many years of experience in the field, and is therefore more than worthy of teaching a course in ergonomics case studies. It's actually quite easy to do well in her class as long as you can apply all that you know about Human Factors.
